INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (45, 1, '2013-11-08 20:04:11', '2013-11-08 20:04:11', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b>Video:Â <a href="http://vimeo.com/37349085">http://vimeo.com/37349085</a></b></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Chasing Victory began in 2011, after 2 long years of reconstructive surgery on founder and master craftsman Jonathan Stroudâ€™s left hand.</p>\n<p>For Jonathan and his wife Lisa, 2009 was going great. Â Jonathan was enjoying his job laying hardwood floors. Â He loved working with his hands, working with wood, and providing financial security for his family. Â The happy couple also saw the arrival of their first child, a beautiful baby girl.</p>\n<p>But two months after Lisa gave birth, Jonathanâ€™s left hand was pulled into an unforgiving table saw. Â Life quickly went from good to bad. Â The table saw not only damaged Jonathanâ€™s hand, but also his sense of purpose and his ability to provide for his family.</p>\n<p>Jonathan looked for any job he could possibly do, but only found hopelessness, depression and loss of confidence. Â As a result, the couples marriage took a huge hit. Â Where there was once adoration and love for one another, there was now Â despair and hatred.</p>\n<p>Determined to provide for his family, Jonathan gave an old idea of his a tryâ€¦wooden rings. Â Though not an easy learning process, the idea was a success. Â For Jonathan, his purpose was reborn. Â Since the incident he had been chasing his victory, and he finally caught it. Â Hopelessness turned to hope, depression turned to joy, and the despair and hatred between him and Lisa turned back to love and adoration. Â Life was good again.</p>\n<p>Today, Jonathan and Lisa believe very strongly in the commitment of marriage. Â Chasing Victory rings are a symbol of that belief. Â To the couple, they serve as a reminder of what their marriage has overcome, and that for every marriage, the best is yet to come.</p>\n<p><i style="line-height:1.5em;">"I work from 5 in the morning to 5 in the evening, creating each ring by hand. Â I also answer each email, take each photo, and package &amp; ship each order. Â After work I play with my daughter, and do my best to be the most loving husband I can be.</i></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><i>This is my story about how Chasing Victory was born from a bad situation that turned around for good. Â I hope it can be an inspiration to you, encouraging you to keep chasing victory.â€</i></p>\n<p><i>-Â </i><i style="line-height:18px;">Jonathan Stroud, Founder &amp; Master Craftsman</i></p>\n<p><i style="line-height:18px;"></i></p>\n\n\n<a href="http://chasingvictory.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/isa_760xN.7002092444_22hv.jpg"><img src="http://chasingvictory.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/isa_760xN.7002092444_22hv.jpg" alt="isa_760xN.7002092444_22hv" /></a>#_gc_file_name_0#\n\n', 'Purpose Reborn', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-08 20:04:11', '2013-11-08 20:04:11', '', 33, 'http://chasingvictory.com/?p=45', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
